 <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>While Salesforce (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRM\" title=\"Salesforce, Inc.\">CRM</a></span>) shares are up roughly 34.61% since the last time I wrote on the software maker, I continue to be bearish on the technology giant on the back</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1025006372/image_1025006372.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742536-salesforce-stock-q3-review-growth-still-slowing-reiterate-strong-sell", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 11:14:10"}, {"id": "4742535", "title": "Bayer's Stock Hits 2-Decade Low: Why It Is A Buy Again", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Sign BAYER on buildings of chemical industry in Leverkusen\" data-id=\"1843440175\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"948px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Fotofantastika</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Bayer AG's (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BAYRY\" title=\"Bayer Aktiengesellschaft\">OTCPK:BAYRY</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BAYZF\" title=\"Bayer Aktiengesellschaft\">OTCPK:BAYZF</a>) stock price continues to decline, and the stock has now dipped below \u20ac20 for the first time in more than 2 decades. <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4712341-bayer-risks-remain-while-business-is-stabilizing\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4712341-bayer-risks-remain-while-business-is-stabilizing\" target=\"_blank\">In my last article</a>, I wrote that the risks</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742535-bayer-stock-hits-two-decade-low-buy-again", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 11:08:22"}, {"id": "4742545", "title": "Culp, Inc. 2025 Q2 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Culp, Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q2 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106057\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742545-culp-inc-2025-q2-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 10:54:52"}, {"id": "4742532", "title": "SPY: Unconventional Economic Proxies Say More Upside", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Lap point of view of man holding tablet\" data-id=\"466457490\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">triloks/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Preamble</strong></h2> <p>Over the years, it seems that government economic indicators have become less and less reliable. Take for instance <a href=\"https://www.shrm.org/mena/topics-tools/news/talent-acquisition/us-employment-gains-revised-down-over-800k-jobs#:~:text=Recent%20U.S.%20jobs%20gains%20weren,the%20BLS'%20annual%20data%20revision.\" rel=\"nofollow\">employment numbers</a>, in August, they were revised downwards by over 800,000, which is quite a sizeable adjustment, if you ask</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742532-spy-unconventional-economic-proxies-say-more-upside", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 10:36:40"}, {"id": "4742540", "title": "F