"Lululemon Athletica Inc.\">LULU</a>) has been battling the skeptics for much of this year. There is still a long way to go, but with the stock now up almost</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/824053452/image_824053452.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742534-lululemon-q3-2024-earnings-update", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 10:03:00"}, {"id": "4742533", "title": "How To Make Sense Of Emerging Market Debt In A Global Portfolio", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Emerging Markets\" data-id=\"1296098015\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4592px\" height=\"3061px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">tum3123</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Damien Buchet, CFA, Chief investment officer, Principal Finisterre</em></p> <p>Emerging market debt (EMD) has garnered increasing attention from investors for many years. While the asset class has historically delivered attractive, diversified returns driven by high income generation, many investors still need help understanding</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1296098015/image_1296098015.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742533-how-to-make-sense-of-emerging-market-debt-in-global-portfolio", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 09:55:00"}, {"id": "4742528", "title": "McDonald's: Investors Will Get A Lot Of Stomach Pain Here", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/id/2148328625/photo/mcdonalds-in-times-square-with-a-crowd-of-people-in-manhattan-in-new-york-city.jpg?b=1&amp;s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=8ockJiN-9yM2xFW0-xqlGQv3brwjAfyy31WdeyFnuLc=\" alt='McDonald\"s in Times Square with a crowd of people in Manhattan in New York City' data-id=\"2148328625\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Jay Mize/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>It's been a great year for U.S. stocks, but one of America's most iconic global brands has not been a participant in this year's rally. McDonald's (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MCD\" title=\"McDonald's Corporation\">MCD</a></span>), the quintessential purveyor of Big Macs</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742528-mcdonalds-stock-investors-rising-labor-costs-operating-margin-decline-sell", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 09:31:02"}, {"id": "4742527", "title": "Tradeweb Government Bond Update - November 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Government bonds memo inscription on the page with calculation.\" data-id=\"1282660847\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5600px\" height=\"3733px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">designer491</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Apart from Japan, global government debt markets reversed October\u2019s sell-off in November, with the five biggest movers all in Europe. The month also saw weak economic data published in the Euro area, starting with the HCOB Flash Eurozone Manufacturing PMI, which dropped to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1282660847/image_1282660847.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742527-tradeweb-government-bond-update-november-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 08:15:00"}]}